## 9. AGENTS.md per-agent

`local/paperclip/AGENTS-dev-primary.md` and `local/paperclip/AGENTS-reviewer.md` stay gitignored. Upload via:

```bash
curl -X PUT -H "Authorization: Bearer $PAPERCLIP_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d "$(jq -Rs '{path:"AGENTS.md",content:.}' < local/paperclip/AGENTS-dev-primary.md)" \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/agents/<dev-primary-N-id>/instructions-bundle/file
```

Iterate AGENTS.md after each poorly-done Issue: what was missing in AGENTS.md that caused the error? Add there instead of fixing manually N times.

