## 10. CI calibration

| PR type | Workflow | Target time | Jobs |
|---|---|---|---|
| `task/* -> feat/*` | `ci-fast-lane.yml` | ~3-4min | lint + typecheck + unit (1 shard, paths-filtered, skip if diff `*.md` only) |
| `feat/* -> dev` | `ci.yml` (full) | ~8min | lint + typecheck + unit (sharded) + contract + build + integration + e2e |
| Push to `main` | `ci.yml` + `deploy.yml` | ~8min CI + smoke | everything above + automatic deploy |

**Approximate arithmetic (30 features/month):**
- Pre-Paperclip: ~24min/feature x 30 = 720min/month baseline.
- Post-Paperclip: 3x task->feat x 3 runs x ~3min + 1x feat->dev x 3 runs x 8min = ~51min/feature x 30 = ~1530min/month.

GitHub Free 2000min/month -> ~470min slack. Configure billing for over-quota ($0.008/min Linux).

**Additional mitigations:**
1. `concurrency: cancel-in-progress: true` in ci-fast-lane (cancels previous run on new push).
2. Aggressive path-filter (skip unit if diff only `*.md`).
3. Skip-if-sha-already-green (auto-merge doesn't re-run if commit has recent green CI).

