## 11. Costs

- **Anthropic subscription** (dev-primary Sonnet, reviewer Opus): flat monthly fee, already paid. **Do not capture per-token** — `budgetMonthlyCents: 0` in Paperclip.
- **Other LLM providers:** zero. Not used in default setup (reviewer is Opus subscription).
- **VPS:** ~$10/mo if dedicated to Paperclip; zero additional if shared with other projects.
- **GitHub Actions:** Free 2000min/month + over-quota billing. Estimated ~1530min/month post-Paperclip.
- **Tailscale:** zero (free tier).

